column1: Here are the allies and enemies columns added for each country:

column7: God's help, the love of the people, Denmark's strength
One for all, all for one
To broadly benefit the human world
If you will it, it is no dream
This is my blissful beloved homeland
With the help of God for Homeland and Freedom
There is no God other than God and Muhammad is the Messenger of God
Always in service with God's guidance
